title: Wii homebrew nub pack (pal twilight hack included)
description:
this pack contains:
- the homebrew channel (Edit: this version of the homebrew channel is outdated, get      the latest one from http://hbc.hackmii.com/download/)
- the homebrew browser
- a quake port for wii (with the pak0 file)
- the twilight hack for PAL wii's

how to use
- place the contents of this directory in the root of your sd card
- do the twilight hack (if you don't know how use this video for help
- choose to install the boot.elf file on your wii

IMPORTANT: this is for PAL version only if you have an ntsc wii you need to download the other version of the twilight hack, visit wiibrew.org for more information. 
I"m NOT responsible if anything happens to your wii (bricks or goes on fire or something like that)
this version DOES work system menu 3.3.
